  "decision_conditions": [
    "The use of the existing, ancillary outbuilding as a separate residential unit would be harmful to the character and appearance of the site, group of buildings and general locality, at odds with the established character and urban grain, resulting in an overdeveloped and cramped form of residential accommodation at both 5 and 5a Carfax Road, all contrary to Policy BE1 of the Hillingdon Local Plan Part 1, Policies DMHD2, DMHB11 and DMHB 12 of the Hillingdon Local Plan Part Two (2020), as well as Policies D4 and D6 of the London Plan (2021).",
    "The applicant has failed to demonstrate a satisfactory policy-led approach to the car and cycle parking provision and layout which could be prejudicial to all road user's safety, contrary to Policy DMT6 of the Hillingdon Local Plan Part Two (2020) and T6 the London Plan (2021).",
    "The proposed self contained unit would provide a poor standard of living for future occupiers, with respect to internal layout, amenity space, privacy and outlook contrary to Policy D6 of the London Plan (2021) and Policy DMHB 16, DMHB 18 and Table 5.1 of the Hillingdon Local Plan Part Two (2020)."
  ],
